"use strict";(self.webpackChunkpos_doc=self.webpackChunkpos_doc||[]).push([[278],{1684(e,t,i){i.r(t),i.d(t,{_pageData:()=>o,default:()=>a});var n=i(641);const o=JSON.parse('{"path":"/guide/notification-tones.html","title":"Notification Tones","lang":"en-US","frontmatter":{"title":"Notification Tones","description":"Set up and configure audio feedback/notification tones in WooCommerce POS to improve checkout speed and minimize errors."},"git":{},"filePathRelative":"guide/notification-tones.md"}'),s={name:"notification-tones.md"},a=(0,i(6262).A)(s,[["render",function(e,t,i,o,s,a){return(0,n.uX)(),(0,n.CE)("div",null,[...t[0]||(t[0]=[(0,n.Fv)('<h1 id="notification-tones" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#notification-tones"><span>Notification Tones</span></a></h1><h2 id="introduction" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#introduction"><span>Introduction</span></a></h2><p>Auditory feedback is a key factor in high-speed point of sale environments. WooCommerce Point of Sale (POS) features an integrated <strong>Notification Tones</strong> system that triggers specific audio cues for core terminal actions.</p><p>By providing instant auditory confirmation, cashiers can process checkouts without having to constantly look at the screen, accelerating throughput and reducing operational mistakes.</p><hr><h2 id="feature-overview" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#feature-overview"><span>Feature Overview</span></a></h2><p>The notification tones system operates automatically on any desktop browser, tablet, or mobile device running the POS. It provides specific audio profiles for the following events:</p><ul><li><strong>Product Selection / Barcode Scan:</strong> A high-pitched, crisp beep sounds immediately when a product is clicked or successfully scanned via a barcode scanner, validating that the item was added to the cart.</li><li><strong>Keypad Tones:</strong> Subdued tactile click tones mimic physical buttons when typing quantities, prices, or customer details, reinforcing fast numeric entry.</li><li><strong>Payment Success Tone:</strong> A clean, satisfying success chime plays once the payment processes successfully and the transaction is finalized.</li><li><strong>Drawer Close Notification:</strong> A soft periodic alert chime plays if a connected cash drawer remains open longer than the configured timeout, reminding cashiers to lock it.</li></ul><p><img src="/pos-for-woocommerce/images/woocommerce-pos/pos-sound.webp" alt="Notification Sounds Settings"></p><p>A short audio confirmation helps streamline checkout workflows by reducing visual reliance on the register screen. Having notification sounds enabled provides instant, eyes-free feedback during checkout, which significantly improves cashier efficiency, speeds up customer throughput, and prevents double-scanning or missed items.</p><hr><h2 id="how-it-works" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#how-it-works"><span>How It Works</span></a></h2><h3 id="enabling-audio-feedback-in-the-pos" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#enabling-audio-feedback-in-the-pos"><span>Enabling Audio Feedback in the POS</span></a></h3><ol><li>Open the POS register interface and log in.</li><li>Navigate to the POS side menu and click <strong>Settings</strong>.</li><li>Locate the <strong>Settings &gt; Audio Settings</strong> panel.</li><li>Toggle the <strong>Sound Feedback (Notification Tones)</strong> option to <strong>On</strong>.</li></ol><hr><h2 id="benefits" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#benefits"><span>Benefits</span></a></h2><ul><li><strong>Faster User Feedback:</strong> Audio cues confirm barcode scans instantly, allowing cashiers to keep their eyes on the packaging and bags.</li><li><strong>Reduced Operational Mistakes:</strong> Double scans or missed items are immediately obvious due to the absence of the corresponding sound cue.</li><li><strong>Sleek Checkout Experience:</strong> Standardized success sounds create a professional checkout rhythm.</li></ul><hr><h2 id="use-cases" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#use-cases"><span>Use Cases</span></a></h2><ul><li><strong>High-Volume Grocery Stores:</strong> Cashiers scan items in rapid succession, using the scanner beep to confirm entry without looking back and forth from the belt to the screen.</li><li><strong>Loud Retail Outlets:</strong> The open drawer chime acts as a security warning, ensuring the cash tray is shut immediately after change is handed out.</li><li><strong>Self-Service Checkouts:</strong> Assist customers using Kiosk checkouts by indicating when an action was completed or requires assistance.</li></ul><hr><h2 id="related-features" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#related-features"><span>Related Features</span></a></h2><ul><li><a href="/woocommerce-pos/dynamic-theme" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">POS Interface Customization</a> — Adjust themes, logos, and layouts alongside sound settings.</li><li><a href="/woocommerce-pos/orders-drawers" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Orders &amp; Checkout Process</a> — Learn how transactions trigger payment confirmations and receipt generation.</li></ul>',23)])])}]])}}]);